128
00:09:36,879 --> 00:09:39,830
But that's less than another occupation.

129
00:09:39,830 --> 00:09:41,209
Astronaut.

130
00:09:41,209 --> 00:09:46,170
An astronaut on the space station for six
months will receive about 80,000 microsieverts

131
00:09:46,170 --> 00:09:47,920
worth of radiation.

132
00:09:47,920 --> 00:09:51,230
But not even they are exposed to the highest
